# .mailmap - Author identity mapping for git history
#
# This file maps commit author names/emails to canonical identities.
# Git tools (git log, git shortlog) and GitHub use this file to
# consolidate contributor attribution.
#
# Format: Canonical Name <canonical@email> Commit Name <commit@email>
#
# Reassign commits originally authored by the "Tgibeast" account
# to the main account "Naxisbeast" (Thapelo Wana).
